The project Bahamut is a full ad-hoc tunneling software to be used by the
Playstation Portable (PSP) to emulate online features.

Currently the following things work:

 * UDP Server
 * Packet capture/inject
 * Bridge interface<=>server
 
Next things to do:

 * TCP session support
 * Auth server
 * Room creation

Dependencies:
 * Linux: libpcap
 * Windows: WinPcap
	
Current developers:

 * Codestation

Last update:  6-Ago-2008 - Codestation
